headline: APS Uses ‘Growth Pays for Growth’ Model to Develop New Natural Gas Plant
summary: PHOENIX, October 30, 2025--Arizona Public Service announced plans to build the Desert Sun Power Plant, a new natural gas facility designed to meet Arizona’s growing needs.
